AWK commands
- search data in file and Print data to stdout 
- find data by patterns 
- format output 
- used on files with bulk data [ searching, conditional execution, updating and filtering ]


Pattern 
# this is a pattern-only statement
awk '/Ori/' empinfo.txt # finds pattern and returns it to stdout

Action
# this is an action-only statement
awk '{ print $1 }' empinfo.txt # represents this first field


